"vnoremap <leader>ru y gv<Esc>`>a<CR><Esc>`<i<CR><Esc>I<esc>g_a_<esc>kJJG()i<esc>p0i.. _<c-o>$: 
"inoremap <leader>ru <esc>bvey gv <Esc>`>a<CR><Esc>`<i<CR><Esc>I<esc>g_a_<esc>kJJG()i<esc>p0i.. _<c-o>$: 


